Text: "My story take part in a city which where I find myself. The story is about\
  \ an exchange student who spend a year on Switzerland. She lives a year with love,\
  \ passions, family , new friends but also bad things. \nIt is a book to reed how\
  \ much a pearson can learn in a year and how difficult it is to go back home after\
  \ that."
